comments: Mathurin (IND) and VanVleet (TOR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Hield (IND) initiates marginal contact to VanVleet's (TOR) front that does not affect his SQBR at the start of the drive.
Turner (IND) fails to establish position outside of the RA prior to body contact occurring with VanVleet (TOR) at the end of his drive.
Nesmith (IND) establishes himself in VanVleet's (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Anunoby (TOR) and Turner (IND) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball in the post.
Turner (IND) is in the lane for less than three seconds when he receives the pass and starts his upward shooting motion.
Siakam (TOR) brings his hands toward Mathurin (IND) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to roll.
Nesmith (IND) legally contests Anunoby's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Turner (IND) holds Poeltl's (TOR) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Siakam (TOR) and Nesmith (IND) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Siakam's (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Siakam (TOR) initiates contact with Turner's (IND) body and arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Turner (IND) and Poeltl (TOR) come together in pursuit of the rebound and marginal contact occurs.
Anunoby (TOR) engages and disengages with Turner (IND) and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Nembhard (IND) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before releasing the jump shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) steps forward and initiates contact with Siakam's (TOR) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
The timeout is awarded to the Pacers before 5 seconds elapses during the inbound.
McConnell (IND) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before the foul occurs.
Anunoby (TOR) initiates contact with McConnell's (IND) arm and affects his SQBR.
Anunoby (TOR) establishes himself in Nembhard's (IND) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Turner (IND) initiates contact with Boucher's (TOR) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on McConnell (IND).
